query:
SELECT 
  name,
  COUNT(*) as count,
  GROUP_CONCAT(id) as ids,
  GROUP_CONCAT(description) as descriptions
FROM achievements
GROUP BY name
HAVING count > 1
ORDER BY count DESC;
